Synopsis:
Yash Raj Filmsâ€™ Saiyaara is an intense love story, that launches Ahaan Panday and Aneet Padda as the next YRF hero and heroine respectively. 

Directed by Mohit Suri, a master of the romance genre, Saiyaara tells a pure-hearted love story of two youngsters Vaani and Krish. While Vaani writes, Krish sings and they both make music together. Though poles apart in their lives, beliefs and backgrounds, Vaani and Krish are perfect with each other and for each other. Will they understand that truth despite their age, their problems? 

They say flawed, imperfect people make for a perfect love storyâ€¦and Saiyaara is about celebrating that one love story that is so deep, so pure and so caring that it is absolutely unconditional.

Vaani and Krish will have to navigate life, their problems, their insecurities to hopefully realise that only love can be the answer to everything. Saiyaara is a film that celebrates every season of love through the eyes of Vaani & Krish and poses a simple questionâ€¦do you love someone so much that you would bet everything to keep that person in your life?

JUJUTSU KAISEN Season 3 is coming exclusively to Crunchyroll January 2026! Watch JUJUTSU KAISEN Crunchyroll! https://got.cr/cc-jjkpv

Yuji Itadori is a boy with tremendous physical strength, though he lives a completely ordinary high school life. One day, to save a classmate who has been attacked by curses, he eats the finger of Ryomen Sukuna, taking the curse into his own soul. From then on, he shares one body with Ryomen Sukuna. Guided by the most powerful of sorcerers, Satoru Gojo, Itadori is admitted to Tokyo Jujutsu High School, an organization that fights the curses... and thus begins the heroic tale of a boy who became a curse to exorcise a curse, a life from which he could never turn back.

Crunchyroll brings you the latest clips, openings, full episodes, and more from your favorite anime!

Kitna chaha tha mujko ye keh jaana
Teri mujhse ye doori me hone nahi deti

Mil Jaye Kya Hi Baat Thi

Han Lagte Hain Mujhko Yeh Kisse Satane
Deta Na Dil Mera Tujhko Bhulane
Adhoore Se Waade Adhoori Si Raatein
Ab Hisse Me Dakhil Mere Bas Woh Yaadein

Rehna Tha Banke Hum-dum Tera
Aise Jana Hi Tha Fir Tu Kyu Thehra
Ab Na Maane Mera Dil 
Ku Na Tere Kabil
Thi Ik Arzoo Ki Main Kehti Rahi Par

Mil Jaye Kya Hi Baat Thi

snippet.description:
For centuries, poets have given voice to the human heart, shaping the language of love. #ArzKiyaHai carries that legacy forward as an intimate tribute rooted in Indiaâ€™s poetic tradition, embracing the unguarded honesty of speaking your heart. At its helm is Indiaâ€™s most popular independent artist, Anuv Jain, pairing delicate guitar work with achingly tender vocals that distill this very emotion into melody. Joining him is Indian electronic duo Lost Stories working their magic on the production of the track as well as performing on the harmonium.
